OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782236890
OL,3,CWoman, 72, guilty of murdering husband
OL,4,Cafter claiming he 'fell on knife'
OL,6,FA woman has been found guilty of
OL,7,Fmurdering her 84-year-old husband
OL,8,Fafter claiming his fatal stab wound
OL,9,Fcame after he fell on a knife.
OL,11,FDaryl Berman, 72, told the authorities
OL,12,Fher husband, David, 84, suffered a
OL,13,Ftragic accident at their home in
OL,14,FPrestwich, Manchester, on 13 March
OL,15,F2025.
OL,17,FA court heard that Mr Berman, who had
OL,18,Fdementia, was found with a stab wound
OL,19,Fto his chest at the couple's home on
OL,20,FButterstile Lane in just before 2pm on
OL,21,F13 March 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
