FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1782236890
OL,3,CWoman, 72, guilty of murdering husband
OL,4,Cafter claiming he 'fell on knife'
OL,6,F"My thoughts are with David Berman's
OL,7,Floved ones at this very difficult
OL,8,Ftime."
OL,10,FMrs Berman, from Bury, will be
OL,11,Fsentenced at a later date.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@FO]
